-1. Match on `Case Number` and current `TO Period`.
-2. If COMP has a pricing element, also match on `SRE Pricing Element`.
-3. If COMP has a blank pricing element and multiple J.1 rows share the same case/period, use the COMP case description as a tie-breaker against J.1 `ICB Case Description`.
